Interface Effect<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    EntityStatusEffect, ParticleEffect, RemoteEffect<T>, SoundEffect, VisualEffect
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TridentEffect, TridentEntityStatusEffect, TridentParticleEffect, TridentRemoteEffect, TridentSoundEffect, TridentVisualEffect

    public interface Effect<T>
    Represents all visual, sound, particle and entity effects

    Author:
